Package: eirm
Type: Package
Title: Explanatory Item Response Modeling for Dichotomous and Polytomous Items
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Okan", "Bulut", email = "bulut@ualberta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID="0000-0001-5853-1267"))
Maintainer: Okan Bulut <bulut@ualberta.ca>
URL: https://github.com/okanbulut/eirm
Description: Analysis of dichotomous and polytomous response data using the explanatory item response modeling framework. Generalized linear mixed modeling is used for estimating the effects of item-related and person-related variables on item responses. 
Depends:
    lme4,
    reshape2,
    optimx
